	<h1 class="title">玩具这么多，为什么橡皮泥这种老产品还卖得很好？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/103970/small/103970.jpg?1431972719" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">朱凯麟 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-02-16 07:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/22292/medium/22292.jpg?1455520517" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="22292" data-title="《玩具这么多，为什么橡皮泥这种老产品还卖得很好？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/22292/medium/22292.jpg?1455520517" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/22292.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
